        rowmax rowmin !*priall !*primat codbexl!* !*prefix !*again
        ops kvarlst cname!* cindex!* optlang!* gentranlang!*
        varlst!* varlst!+ !*outstk!* !*optdecs !*inputc !*vectorc
        !*intern min!-expr!-length!*)$

